in the case we are dealing with here, the players were not to aim to avoid the granting of the punishment (which would be a clear case of circumventing the rules), but rather chose to submit to it.
They made a strategic decision without avoiding or fleeing punishment.
Although the line between wit and circumvention of the rules is not entirely clear, I believe that in this case it was clearly a wit.
